Search Icon Created with sketchtool. A Military Themed Super Bowl Commercial Aired AFTER The Game And Most Of Us Missed It posted by Brooke Taylor - 
Most of us watch the big game for the commercials and it's a shame that this is one that most of us probably missed.. because it was definitely the most powerful. 
Grab a tissue and get ready for chill bumps. These soldiers couldn’t be home for #SuperBowl , so we brought home to them. pic.twitter.com/BZR8RyeSMu — Hyundai USA (@Hyundai) February 6, 2017 Family is the most important thing in the world to me, I have 3 brothers, two sisters and my parents have been married for over 30 years (GO MOM & DAD!)
